divs: Sighting DetailsTo Whom It May Concern: I took this footage while on a hike in keremeos bc. i was doing a big hike in remote wilderness i was at about 8,000-8,500ft elevation. It was a 15 hr day of hiking. At the time I wasn't aware that I had filmed anything out of the ordinary. I noticed it while showing the video to my family. I've watched it frame by frame and still havn't come to any conclusion as to what it is. The file names are the times that it appears. It happens real fast so look real close.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Keremeos
This sighting has never been favorited.
